heading: Part songs, Sacred.
general-note: Here are entered collections of sacred part songs in several languages or in Latin. Collections of sacred part songs entirely in a language other than Latin, and individual sacred part songs in other languages, are assigned an additional heading for part songs qualified by the language, e.g.. Part songs, English..
Sacred part songs in specific forms are entered under the form, e.g.. Anthems; Motets;. etc..
